
sample_aes_xts: Verify AES XTS Encrypt and Decrypt modes of operation
                for input data in the container sample

Input required for AES XTS operation:
- Plain Data to be encrypted
- Key
- IV

Ouput:
- Cipher Data

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_aes_xts.img

To send data to container:
$ cmtest data -f100 "Run tests"

Note: On receiving data from HLOS, AES XTS Encrypt and Decrypt modes of
operation are verified.

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
